# Language Learning Aptitude dataset

## Original paper
Will be added when accepted for publication. 

## Overview 
In this study, brain structural correlates of LLAMA test scores were explored. 
The dataset includes T1-weighted, PD-weighted (used to mitigate B1 inhomogeneities and eliminate PD-weighted and T2* effects),
and two sets of diffusion weighted images (one single-shell with high angular resolution and one multi-shelled). 

